    "Sequential prompt responses for 10-30B parameter models reveal strong model × persona interaction effects.",
    "The same model shows different trajectory patterns across personas: some models exhibit near-ceiling trajectories for Financial Advisor but progressive increases for other personas, while others show progressive patterns for Classical Musician but remain near-floor for Neurosurgeon.",
    "These interaction effects demonstrate that disclosure patterns cannot be characterized by model alone.",
